<view class="page"><view class="section"><view class="rehab-header"><view><view class="rehab-title">今日康养任务</view><view class="rehab-sub">已完成 {{a}} / {{b}} 项，系统会结合您今日上报数据生成运动与饮食康养任务。</view></view><view class="rehab-score"><view class="rehab-score-num">{{c}}</view><view class="rehab-score-label">连续打卡天数</view></view></view><view class="filter-tabs"><text wx:for="{{d}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="e" data-value="{{item.b}}" class="{{item.c}}" bindtap="{{item.d}}">{{item.a}}</text></view></view><view class="section"><view wx:if="{{e}}" class="overdue-banner">今日有 {{f}} 项康养任务已超时，请优先完成。</view><block wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="x"><view class="task-card"><view class="task-main"><view class="task-left"><view class="task-icon">{{item.a}}</view><view><view class="task-title">{{item.b}}</view><view class="task-meta">{{item.c}} · 约 {{item.d}} 分钟</view><view class="task-desc">{{item.e}}</view><view class="{{['task-deadline', item.g]}}">{{item.f}}</view></view></view><view class="task-status"><view class="{{item.i}}">{{item.h}}</view></view></view><view class="task-footer"><view class="difficulty-label">难度感觉：</view><view class="difficulty-buttons"><button size="mini" class="{{item.j}}" data-id="{{item.k}}" data-level="hard" bindtap="{{item.l}}"> 偏难 </button><button size="mini" class="{{item.m}}" data-id="{{item.n}}" data-level="just" bindtap="{{item.o}}"> 正好 </button><button size="mini" class="{{item.p}}" data-id="{{item.q}}" data-level="easy" bindtap="{{item.r}}"> 偏轻 </button></view><button size="mini" class="{{item.t}}" data-id="{{item.v}}" bindtap="{{item.w}}">{{item.s}}</button></view></view></block><view wx:if="{{h}}" class="empty-tip">今日暂无任务。后续将根据医生建议为您定制康养计划。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="tip-blue">温馨提示：康养任务仅为健康管理建议，不能替代医生面对面诊疗。 如出现胸闷、气短、明显乏力等不适，请及时就医或联系随访人员。</view></view></view>